s.CONS:- Old graphics.- Some countries names and flags are outdated.- Sometimes some countries won't attack you or even bothering defending if you have an extremely strong military.- Infantry units are effectively useless.- Requires a lot of concentration and effort.- Multiplayer has very few players.Overall, very good game but requires a lot of concentration. 9/10."
