76561198007956161,Not Recommended,282400,16152435,"Posted: 3 June, 2015",all,jobro_06,"Overall a good game, but what kills it for me is that you spend hours and hours playing it, only to be beaten not by other countries but by the infamous ""Autarky Bug"". Incase for those who don't know what it is, it is basically a bug that comes later on during the game where everyone or most of the world's countries have become self sufficient and hence no longer want to buy anything on the world market. In simple terms, when all the world's countries produce everything they want ""meet their demands"", they no longer want to buy from you. This in turn causes your economy/personal income to slowly deplete/decrease over time. The bug basically sends you back to the stone age and apparently there is no other way around this bug just yet.So for those thinking about buying this game, don't do it till they fix the ""Autarky bug"". Otherwise its your money down the drain as I've found out."
